Package: neurocluster
Type: Package
Title: Spatially Constrained Clustering for Neuroimaging Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Bradley",
                  family = "Buchsbaum",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com")
Description: Provides multiple algorithms for spatially constrained clustering
    of 3D and 4D neuroimaging data. Methods include supervoxels, SNIC (Simple
    Non-Iterative Clustering), SLIC (Simple Linear Iterative Clustering),
    slice-based minimum spanning forest, FLASH-3D with DCT compression, and
    adaptive correlation superclustering (ACSC). All methods balance feature
    similarity and spatial proximity to produce coherent brain parcellations.
    A unified 'cluster4d' interface standardizes access to all algorithms.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
